Filed, original amended information; copy served on defendant.  Defendant acknowledges receipt of information, waives formal reading, pleads not guilty. On motion of the State, Court ordered charge amended to:
Count 1: First Degree Intentional Homicide, Use of a Dangerous Weapon, contrary to Wisconsin Statutes section(s) 940.01(1)(a), 939.50(3)(a), 939.63(1)(b), a Class A Felony;
Count 2: Possession of aFirearm by a Felon, contrary to Wisconsin Statutes section(s) 941.29(2)(a), 939.50(3)(g), a Class G Felony.
